                                                 [sudo-user creation]
1. useradd masthan    [whenever we create user "group & folder" automatically created]
2. passwd masthan
   ** ** ** [give password]
3. visudo (or) vim /etc/sudoers (line-100)
   masthan    ALL=(ALL)       ALL
4. su - masthan 
   sudo useradd baji (if we can create user it's working)
5. 

commands:
cat /etc/passwd  : to show list of users
cat /etc/group	 : to show list of groups
userdel Vijay    : to delete Vijay user
groupdel Vijay   : to delete Vijay group
   


